original:
<font face='$HandwrittenFont' size = "18">
I've heard around that you're quite the fighter in Skyrim. We need more people like you here. Too many milk drinkers these days. Since you seem like the fighting type, I'll let you in on something. If you want some more action, there is a brawling tournament that is happening in Skyrim. We'll see how good you actually are.
If you want in on the action, talk to any of these people:

- Maul in Riften
- Falion in Morthal
- Niranye in Windhelm

- The Organizer
string:
<font face='$HandwrittenFont' size = "18">
我听说你在天际可是个颇有名气的战士。我们这里需要更多像你这样的人，现在太多软弱无能的家伙。你看起来很喜欢打架，我就告诉你一个好消息吧。如果想接受更多的挑战，天际最近将举办一场格斗大赛。到时候我们就来瞧瞧你到底有多厉害。
如果你想要参一脚，请与下列的其中一位交谈：

- 裂谷城，摩尔
- 莫萨尔城，法利昂
- 风舵城，妮兰雅

- 主办者

original:
<font face="$HandwrittenBold" size="18">
How dare they!

He thinks I'm not good enough to join their little tournament! The audacity! I've been brawling my whole life. Just because that lizard got a lucky hit on me. I will show them! I will show all those fools!

他们怎么敢！

他们认为我不够资格参加他们的小比赛！好大的胆子！我打了一辈子的架。那只蜥蜴不过是幸运的打中我一拳而已。我要让他们瞧瞧！让那些蠢货好好见识一下！
</font>
